@Video(source: ResourceReference, alt: String?, poster: ResourceReference?) {
    ...
} Parameters sourceThe name and file extension of a video in your Swift framework or package project. (required)

The name and file extension of an image in your Swift framework or package project. This image serves as a poster image for the video and shows when the video isn’t playing. (required)

The Video directive displays a video in your tutorial. Provide the name of a video and the name of a poster image to show when the video isn’t playing.
